'''痕跡器官'''（{{lang-en|vestigial organ}}），是指[[生物|生物]]經過[[進化|進化]]後為了[[適應|適應]][[環境|環境]]，較不需要的[[器官|器官]]會漸漸退化，直到失去{{le|功能 (生物學)|Function_(biology)|功能}}。但仍殘存在[[生物體|生物體]]可作為[[生物演化|生物演化]]的證據。<ref name="DelahousseMeganck2009">{{cite book|author1=Bernard Delahousse|author2=Martin Meganck|title=Engineering in Context|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=MUz3qg3uB0UC&pg=PA270|year=2009|publisher=Academica|isbn=978-87-7675-700-7|pages=270|accessdate=2015-10-21|archive-date=2017-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170119002158/https://books.google.com/books?id=MUz3qg3uB0UC&pg=PA270|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://biobar.hbhcgz.cn/Article/ShowArticle.asp?ArticleID=16666 |title = 痕迹器官 |date = 2011-04-06 |accessdate = 2014-07-16 |quote = 痕迹器官不仅提供了生物进化的证据，也有助于确定生物进化所经历的途径。 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140720103130/http://biobar.hbhcgz.cn/Article/ShowArticle.asp?ArticleID=16666 |archive-date = 2014-07-20 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>

